To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private MorningStar _morningstar;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_morningstar = MorningStar(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_morningstar.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "period", _morningstar.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "morningstar", _morningstar.Current);
}
